a guy with a weapon." There's much back and

00:39:44.310 --> 00:39:48.160
forth between two helicopters and ground troops
and armored vehicles nearby.

00:39:48.160 --> 00:39:54.380
"Have 5 to 6 individuals with AK-47s. Request
permission to engage. Roger that. We have

00:39:54.380 --> 00:39:59.580
