free to engage. Over." The helicopter circles

00:39:59.580 --> 00:40:03.800
around with the crosshairs squarely in the
center of the eight men. Wikileaks and its

00:40:03.800 --> 00:40:10.190
partner for the story, the Icelandic National
Broadcasting Service, added subtitles to the

00:40:10.190 --> 00:40:15.530
