Reuters workers were. Sustained automatic

00:40:15.530 --> 00:40:20.770
weapon fire erupts; most of the men are killed
instantly. Noor-Eldeen runs away, and the

00:40:20.770 --> 00:40:28.100
crosshairs follow him shooting non-stop until
he falls dead. The radio transmission continues.

00:40:28.100 --> 00:40:32.970
